etymology:
Unknown. According to one explanation:
* Literally, “to pull a thirty-one”, a tabooistic alteration of el çekmek (“to masturbate”, literally “to pull a hand”), dating back to Ottoman times, when ال (el, “hand”) could be interpreted with abjad numerals as 31, by the sum of ا, which refers to 1, and ل, which refers to 30.
